      Yan, is there a reason the Galactors arent on the site?


       Tarantulas sees the jets coming on his viewscreen. The radar picks up 
the missles shot by Supernove instantly and responded with four quick laser 
blasts from the turrets. The missles exploded before reaching the shield, 
sending debris flying this way and that.
       The Vycir/Slasys' laser fire battered the shield, but didnt drain to 
much power. The EMP canon released five silvery blasts swirling at high speed 
towrds the jet.
       "A joint attack heh?" Tarantulas says to himself in almost a chuckle. 
"Let them try! This base will stop them all. The Iron Fist couldnt penetrate 
this base." He sent word to Hell Beast of Zardus' plans.

       Nighteyes and Craken continue to monitor the frequency patterens and 
radio traffic of the Black Fortress, and recive Zardus' transmission. "Looks 
like Zardus has an agenda." She says, looking at Craken.
       "Our base will hold itself well. Bots like Zardus can only send 
obsticles. It is us who must over come them." He replied. His white eyes were 
distant somehow.
